Python 
——— ALL LOWERCASE———

pip install django          —— to install django to the project
django-admin startproject [projectname] .         —— create package/ directory (app)
django-admin startapp [appname] —— add app
python3 manage.py runserver    —— run server
Python3 manage.py runserver 0.0.0.0:5000. — to run in custom port [5000 - port number]


{Project Setting Below Installed_App}

EXTERNAL_APP = [
‘accounts’,
‘home’
]

INSTALLED_APPS += EXTERNAL_APPS

————— (App name like home, accounts, products, etc)
Also in django.filter is install 
‘django_filters’

python3 manage.py makemigrations — make model to db
pythion3 manage.py migrate. ——to save to db

python3 manage.py shell       ——to enter shell

python3 manage.py createsuperuser   — to create first admin

Pip install django.filter


